  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy of Overnight Closed Loop in Children With Type 1Diabetes Mellitus in Luxembourg</brief_title>
  <official_title>Open Label Single Center Randomized Cross Over Study to Validate Current Algorithms and Evaluate Safety and Efficacy of Closed Loop Insulin Delivery (FlorenceD2 System) in Children With Type 1 Diabetes Between 6 - 12 Years of Age</official_title>
  <sponsors>
