  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to validate current algorithms and evaluate safety and efficacy
      of overnight closed loop insulin delivery (FlorenceD2 system) in children with type 1
      diabetes between 6 - 12 years of age in Luxembourg .
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
